MediaWiki extension CategoryBrowser, version 0.3.1

* download the latest available version and extract it to your wiki extension directory. 
* add the following line to LocalSettings.php 
require_once( "$IP/extensions/CategoryBrowser/CategoryBrowser.php" );
* check out Special:Version page to verify the installation 

See http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:CategoryBrowser for further details.